extendedInfo.detail: Dig into a dish the whole family will enjoy with SpaghettiOså¨ Canned Pasta with Meatballs. Each delicious bite of this canned pasta and meatballs features the classic o-shaped pasta you know and love to add some fun to any snack. This canned pasta puts a yummy spin on original SpaghettiOså¨ with the addition of savory meatballs, making it a delicious part of any meal. One cup of SpaghettiOså¨ canned pasta with meatballs contains 1/2 cup of vegetables, as well as 11 grams of protein for a healthy snack or lunch you can feel good about. Break out this convenient canned food when you're craving tasty snacks, or prepare it as a healthy entree for a fun kids lunch. This microwave pasta is ready in as little as 3 minutes. Just heat in a microwave-safe bowl on high for 1 1/2 to 2 minutes, let stand for 1 minute, then stir. Or, cook up this fun-loving pasta on the stove. The can is recyclable for easy disposal. Add character to every bite with SpaghettiOså¨: the neat round spaghetti you can eat with a spoon. Questions or comments? Call us at 1-800-Pasta-02. campbells.com/spaghettios.
